flowchart LR
  U[User / Sarthi] --> M[Main Agent]
  M --> P[Planner]

  subgraph DEV[On-Device Control Plane (No Sandbox)]
    M
    P
    MOD[Moderator]
    JAN[Janitor]
    ARC[Architect]
    SIGNER[Host TX Signer\n(key custody)]
    MEM[(Memory)]
    CRON[(Cron)]
    AUD[(Audit/State)]
  end

  subgraph SBX[Sandbox Zone]
    direction TB
    RSBX[Research Sandbox]
    CSBX[Coder Sandbox]
    TXSBX[TX Sandbox\n(no key material)]
    AFSBX[Antfarm Swarm Sandbox]
  end

  P --> RSBX
  P --> CSBX
  P --> TXSBX
  P --> AFSBX

  TXSBX -->|sign request via unix socket| SIGNER
  SIGNER -->|signature only| TXSBX

  MOD --> M
  ARC --> M
  M --> JAN
  M --> MEM
  M --> AUD
  M --> CRON

  style SIGNER fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#b91c1c,stroke-width:2px
  style TXSBX fill:#fff1f2,stroke:#b91c1c,stroke-width:2px
  style ARC fill:#ede9fe,stroke:#6d28d9,stroke-width:2px
  style SBX fill:#eef7ff,stroke:#2563eb,stroke-width:1px
